@startuml sequence_diagram_test_division

participant "Pytest Framework" as Pytest
participant "calc() fixture" as Fixture
participant "Calculator" as Calc

== Happy Path: divide returns a result ==

Pytest -> Fixture : invoke calc() fixture
activate Fixture
Fixture -> Calc : Calculator()
activate Calc
Fixture --> Pytest : Calculator instance
deactivate Fixture

Pytest ->> Calc : divide(a, b)
Calc --> Pytest : float result
deactivate Calc

Pytest -> Pytest : assert result == expected
note right : assertion passes

== Exception Path: divide by zero ==

Pytest -> Fixture : invoke calc() fixture
activate Fixture
Fixture -> Calc : Calculator()
activate Calc
Fixture --> Pytest : Calculator instance
deactivate Fixture

Pytest ->> Calc : divide(10, 0)
Calc --> Pytest : raise ZeroDivisionError
deactivate Calc

Pytest -> Pytest : pytest.raises() catches ZeroDivisionError
note right : assertion passes

@enduml
